OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA wet and windy day as rain
OL,6,Fspreads across the region, turning
OL,7,Flocally heavy at times, particularly
OL,8,Fover the hills. Feeling muggy under
OL,9,Fwidespread cloud cover and patchy hill
OL,10,Ffog. Winds becoming strong and gusty
OL,11,Fduring the afternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FOutbreaks of rain becoming
OL,14,Fincreasingly showery into the evening,
OL,15,Fhowever heavy bursts are still
OL,16,Fpossible. Drier late in the night with
OL,17,Fsome clear spells developing. Widely
OL,18,Fwindy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
