OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FLargely cloudy and breezy on
OL,6,FFriday with patchy rain, however the
OL,7,Frain may turn heavier for a time
OL,8,Facross the north and east of the
OL,9,Fregion later.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FFurther
OL,12,Fshowers possible on Saturday.
OL,13,FOtherwise becoming increasingly
OL,14,Fsettled on Sunday with drier and
OL,15,Fwarmer conditions developing. Similar
OL,16,Fon Monday perhaps feeling very warm in
OL,17,Fthe sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
